title: SNL’s ‘Gym Class’ skit is so stupid that you can’t help but laugh | For The Win
text:
Follow @LukeKerrDineen 
What I’d have given to be a fly on the wall for the planning of this skit. What do you think happened, exactly? Saturday Night Live had like three minutes to kill, didn’t know what to do, so cooked up the simplest idea ever. 
“ What if we just had a guy fart a lot?” 
So stupid. So very stupid. But, don’t lie: You laughed a little bit, right? More Sports!
